title: 10/14: Weekend Recap - Jameis was Good, Oakland was Bad (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Let's recap Sunday's action! The stud RBs were great again (2:00) and we catch you up on big news (4:44) including our thoughts on Dalvin Cook, Leonard Fournette and other injured stars. Then we've got winners (8:00) like Alex Collins and Mitchell Trubisky and losers (17:00) like Mike Williams and every Raider ... Worryometer (25:30) for three stud WRs who have been disappointing lately, Buy or Sell (28:15) for Eric Ebron, the CHI RBs, Frank Gore and more. Then a look at the Week 6 leaders (34:35) at each position ... Recapping every game (44:22) with Fantasy thoughts. Pick up Chris Godwin! We're encouraged by Doug Baldwin's performance. David Njoku is set up for a nice stretch ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
This episode is sponsored by www.ZipRecruiter.com
